::GoldenEye::

She looked at him and smiled. "Well then, I shall return shortly."
She transformed into eagle mode and flew off, leaving him in the 
grove of trees.

She flew high in the twilight of the evening. She soared on the warm 
air currents and floated in the breeze. She looked down and searched 
the landscape for some prey.  She saw a fat gopher and swooped down 
and caught it in her talons.   She flew up with her catch and flew 
back to the grove of trees where Dollen was.  She put the gopher 
infront of him and transformed back to bot mode.

She smiled, "It's not much, but it will have to do for now.  Until 
the night creatures come out, it's slim pickings."  She picked up the 
gopher and pulled out a small energon blade.  She expertly skinned 
and dressed the animal for dinner.
